      "layout": "The page primarily uses a full-bleed layout for its immersive background gradients, with content contained within a consistent max-width of 1078px, centered on the screen. The hero section features a large, centered headline directly on the animated gradient background. Sections maintain a consistent vertical rhythm, with generous section gaps of 46px. Content elements are typically stacked or arranged in minimal two-column text-left/image-right patterns (where 'image' refers to the abstract gradient visuals), but all elements appear to live within the main content well. The header is a sticky top navigation bar with minimal text links.",
